description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim sit down with the very kind, Eric Stonestreet (Modern Family, The Secret Life of Pets, Bad Teacher)! They talk about ghosting friends, anatomy, Eric's new show "The Toy Box" and how a broken heart got him to audition for his first play! They do a few Deal-Breakers then call Jack, who’s having issues with an aggressive ex, and Hannah, who’s boyfriend is embarrassed to introduce her to his parents because of her tattoos.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
